post_text:
FCEMF Softball will be heading to Centennial for a triangular on Aug. 22nd. Admission will be $6 for adults and $4 for students. Concessions will be provided by A1 Southern Cooking. Games times are 12:00 PM - Bishop Neumann vs. FCEMF & 2:00 PM - Centennial vs. FCEMF.
COVID EXPECTATIONS:
-Social distancing is required
-Masks are encouraged
-Please bring chairs as bleacher space will be limited
-Social distance in dugouts (can use bleachers for more room)
-When team is done playing, please have fans clear out for next team’s fans to sit
-Only 2 per restroom at a time
-Playground equipment use is at the risk of the parents
-Only food allowed is either from A1 Southern Cooking or prepackaged foods (sack lunches)
